OL,3,C'History is repeating itself': Dozens
OL,4,Cof displaced islanders without home in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FMore than 50 displaced Chagos
OL,8,Fislanders have been sleeping on the
OL,9,Ffloor of a leisure centre after
OL,10,Farriving at Gatwick Airport this week.
OL,12,FThey were granted UK citizenship after
OL,13,Fthey were forced to leave their
OL,14,Fhomeland, Diego Garcia, in the 1960s
OL,15,Fand 70s when the British bought the
OL,16,FChagos islands.
