OL,3,C'History is repeating itself': Dozens
OL,4,Cof displaced islanders without home in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FThe land was bought to become an
OL,8,FAmerican military base, but it lead to
OL,9,Fthousands of people being caught up in
OL,10,Fan expulsion and becoming stranded in
OL,11,FMauritius.
OL,13,FIn 2022, the government launched the
OL,14,FBritish Overseas Territories
OL,15,FCitizenship scheme, meaning
OL,16,FChagossians can get a British
OL,17,Fpassport, which many have already
OL,18,Ftaken up.
