OL,7,FCampaigner, Misley Mandarin said: "We
OL,8,Fall know in the UK there is a housing
OL,9,Fcrisis. But the local authorities need
OL,10,Fto find us a place to go because we're
OL,11,Fgoing to be in the street. We feel
OL,12,Fwe've been deported in the 60s and
OL,13,F70s, and history is repeating itself."
OL,15,FCrawley Town Council said in a
OL,16,Fstatement on its website: "For the
OL,17,FChagossian people, a deep sense of
OL,18,Finjustice remains.
