OL,13,F"The protests had the effect of making
OL,14,Fhousing assessment decisions
OL,15,Fchallenging. Staff from both Crawley
OL,16,FBorough Council and West Sussex County
OL,17,FCouncil responded both professionally
OL,18,Fand compassionately in meeting that
OL,19,Fchallenge.
